Topper 20 is a scholarship program for the students appearing for IIT JEE . It is a two year program which includes free mentorship along with free fooding and lodging by Parmanu Classes, Patna, Bihar. Students who want to apply for this Scholarship program have to register for the Topper 20 Competitive exam that is to be held as per the dates announced by Parmanu. Since it is a two year program, only those students who are appearing in class 10th Board are eligible for Topper20 Final selection.

i-Prepare is a digital education joint initiative by the Department of Skill Development, IRCTC in collaboration with Bodvid Pvt. Ltd. to Train and Educate learners from various backgrounds and sectors in essential skills required in the modern world. i-Prepare is an Ai enabled app which guesses a learner\'s doubt in real time and solves them instantly. IRCTC is coming up with various courses for Internal staffs, Vendor Staffs and for General public.
